# Build-context exclusions (ci-cd-and-testing.md §2.2): keep the Docker build
# context minimal AND secret-free. T-04-04A mitigation — .git history, every .env
# variant, tests, and local runtime state must never enter an image layer.

# ── VCS / CI metadata ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes
.github
.planning

# ── Secrets / local config (NEVER into a layer) ───────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key

# ── Tests + test artifacts ────────────────────────────────────────────
**/tests
**/test-results
**/playwright-report
**/blob-report
**/.playwright

# ── Python local state ────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/__pycache__
**/*.py[cod]
**/.venv
**/venv
**/.mypy_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/.pytest_cache
**/*.egg-info

# ── Node / frontend local state ───────────────────────────────────────
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.vite
**/*.local

# ── Databases / runtime state ─────────────────────────────────────────
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
**/*.db
/data

# ── Design handoff bundle + docs not needed in an image ───────────────
design
docs

# ── Editor / OS cruft ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.idea
.vscode
*.swp

# ── Existing Dockerfiles / compose (not part of the app image content) ─
Dockerfile.*
.dockerignore
docker-compose*.yml
